{"doc":{"isMarkdown":true,"isTranslated":true,"isActive":true,"flaws":{},"title":"物件導向程式設計","mdn_url":"/zh-TW/docs/Glossary/OOP","locale":"zh-TW","native":"正體中文 (繁體)","sidebarHTML":"","body":[{"type":"prose","value":{"id":null,"title":null,"isH3":false,"content":"<p><strong>物件導向程式設計</strong>（Object-Oriented Programming、OOP）是一種程式設計方法。其將資料封裝（encapsulate）於物件（<strong><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Glossary/Object\">objects</a></strong>）中，我們需透過物件間接操作這些被封裝的內部資料，而非直接操作資料本身。</p>\n<p><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Glossary/JavaScript\">JavaScript</a>為重度物件導向語言，其遵循 <strong>prototype-based model</strong>（<a href=\"/en-US/docs/Web/JavaScript/Inheritance_and_the_prototype_chain#class-based_vs._prototype-based_languages\" class=\"only-in-en-us\" title=\"Currently only available in English (US)\">與 class-based 相對 (en-US)</a>）</p>"}},{"type":"prose","value":{"id":"相關文章","title":"相關文章","isH3":false,"content":"<ul>\n  <li>維基百科上的 <a href=\"https://zh.wikipedia.org/wiki/%E7%89%A9%E4%BB%B6%E5%B0%8E%E5%90%91%E7%A8%8B%E5%BC%8F%E8%A8%AD%E8%A8%88\" class=\"external\" rel=\" noopener\">物件導向程式設計</a></li>\n  <li><a href=\"/zh-TW/docs/Learn/JavaScript/Objects\">Introduction to object-oriented JavaScript</a></li>\n</ul>"}}],"toc":[{"text":"相關文章","id":"相關文章"}],"summary":"物件導向程式設計（Object-Oriented Programming、OOP）是一種程式設計方法。其將資料封裝（encapsulate）於物件（objects）中，我們需透過物件間接操作這些被封裝的內部資料，而非直接操作資料本身。","popularity":0,"modified":"2022-10-01T03:41:16.000Z","other_translations":[{"title":"OOP","locale":"en-US","native":"English (US)"},{"title":"Programación orientada a objetos","locale":"es","native":"Español"},{"title":"POO","locale":"fr","native":"Français"},{"title":"OOP (オブジェクト指向プログラミング)","locale":"ja","native":"日本語"},{"title":"OOP","locale":"ko","native":"한국어"},{"title":"OOP","locale":"pt-BR","native":"Português (do Brasil)"},{"title":"ООП","locale":"ru","native":"Русский"},{"title":"OOP","locale":"zh-CN","native":"中文 (简体)"}],"source":{"folder":"zh-tw/glossary/oop","github_url":"https://github.com/mdn/translated-content/blob/ma